00:04.463 --> 00:07.006
<i>Warden Lacy, he told me</i>

00:07.007 --> 00:09.008
<i>he had always thought the Devil</i>

00:09.009 --> 00:11.844
<i>was just a metaphor, but now he knew</i>

00:11.845 --> 00:14.263
<i>the Devil was a boy.</i>

00:14.264 --> 00:15.641
Shit!

00:17.267 --> 00:19.060
<i>There's an offer on the table.</i>

00:19.061 --> 00:21.103
<i>The prison wants to cap punitive damages</i>

00:21.104 --> 00:22.897
<i>in exchange for letting you walk.</i>

00:22.898 --> 00:24.899
I say we employ the tried-and-true

00:24.900 --> 00:27.236
legal strategy of "Go fuck yourself."

00:28.176 --> 00:29.946
<i>I adopted a black son.</i>

00:29.947 --> 00:31.322
It's me. I'm Henry.

00:31.323 --> 00:33.491
Yeah. 'Course you are.

00:33.492 --> 00:35.034
<i>- Where is he?
- Who?</i>

00:35.035 --> 00:37.161
<i>- My father.
- They moved him</i>

00:37.162 --> 00:40.039
to a yard up in Bangor by the airport.

00:40.040 --> 00:41.916
<i>Henry Matthew Deaver.</i>

00:41.917 --> 00:44.835
<i>Big mess with the state police
when he was a kid,</i>

00:44.836 --> 00:46.546
<i>pulled some stunt, ran away from home...</i>

00:46.547 --> 00:48.965
<i>people thought somebody took him.</i>

00:48.966 --> 00:51.217
No frostbite.

00:51.218 --> 00:52.970
You been inside somewhere?

